This directory holds files of the BCPL system in compressed
encoded form generated by the xcencode command.

cintsys-files is the list of files to encode.

make all   create the encoded file cintsys.xc

bmakefile is used by bmake running under VMS to convert the file
cintsys.xc to something suitable for xcdecode. The converted file is
called cintsys.xc1.

This file is expanded on the target machine using the command 

bmake decodeall

in directory distribution/BCPL.

make SONY8GB
make HPA8GB         Both copy the directory sysxfiles to a memory stick